  "summary": "Important: xz security update",
  "details": "XZ Utils is an integrated collection of user-space file compression utilities based on the Lempel-Ziv-Markov chain algorithm (LZMA), which performs lossless data compression. The algorithm provides a high compression ratio while keeping the decompression time short.\nSecurity Fix(es):\n* gzip: arbitrary-file-write vulnerability (CVE-2022-1271)\nFor more details about the security issue(s), including the impact, a CVSS score, acknowledgments, and other related information, refer to the CVE page(s) listed in the References section.",
